title: Daz3D - Poser - Street Dance For Genesis 3 Male and Female
description:
--- previously uploaded to KAT by 111jack ---

Street Dance is a cool and sporty set of conforming clothing that comes in four parts: top, sleeve, pants and shoes, for both Genesis 2 Female(s) and Genesis 3 Female(s).

All part are carefully UV-mapped and are covered by two texture templates. This will be helpful if you want to explore your own texturing ideas
